    <h3>3-Year Academic Program</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Year 1: Foundations in Bible & Doctrine</li>
      <li>Year 2: Homiletics, Evangelism & Church Planting 1–2</li>
      <li>Year 3: Church Planting 3, Expository Preaching & Electives</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>4th Year Internship</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>15 units Supervised Ministry</li>
      <li>Ministry Reflection Journal & Suggestion Paper</li>
      <li>Panel Evaluation & Graduation Chapel</li>
    </ul>
